rows.label: qev092505_MSG0001
rows.name: Lin's design is very exciting, is it not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092505_MSG0002
rows.name:
Even us Ma-non would never think of this, you know?
I can't wait for those materials to get here so so we
can see it take a maiden flight...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092505_MSG0003
rows.name:
I never thought the repairs could be done in one day,
did you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092505_MSG0004
rows.name:
But working alongside Lin lit a super fire inside me
or something? It's like my my hands started moving at
hyperspeed...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092505_MSG0005
rows.name:
Isobe is making a show of staying cool, but you can
tell he's jumping up and down and shrieking on the
inside, right? What a nice guy. And a great engineer![ST:wait ]
